{"tid":565494,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"佢係年三十晚搞大我個肚","createTime":"2018-02-19T04:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T12:43:28.000Z","uid":53003,"like":54,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"688a27b568ac209e3ef193099f5afd3eceb95a5d","tid":565494,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"佢年三十黎我屋企，買了鮑魚，龍蝦，青蟹，花膠，海參，雞，燒腩，燒鵝，石班，豆苗，屋企人都讚佢識做人。咁我同佢入廚房一齊煮團年飯餸，足十大碟，好豐富又好好味，食得過量搞到個肚都漲。不過好開心，因為屋企人對他印象改觀。<br />\n<br />\n之後佢入我房傾計，我摸佢個肚都係食到漲，大家哈哈笑。"},{"pid":"053286362a51b7de029991867682f4a925b5767e","tid":565494,"uid":20449,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:39:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a14f29eb7f1b15154677ec5510ca588af617acb8","tid":565494,"uid":6060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"房內裏總是充滿快樂的空氣"},{"pid":"51e76dcc62ebe48487424fa35c65ea2b3d11b0e1","tid":565494,"uid":144529,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"我認我心邪"},{"pid":"a1d9ecfdef7d66af48eb10f2d9a1ce399a59197d","tid":565494,"uid":62011,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:16:20.000Z","msg":"十個月後，你生左堆鮑魚，龍蝦，青蟹，花膠，海參，雞，燒腩，燒鵝，石班，豆苗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba07664b3d4561a5aec880ed85d2452a16f260ac","tid":565494,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"買盤菜仲好啦<br />\n<br />\n多鳩餘"},{"pid":"1d574efb8ae3cc0c6e113d3c60daeec34cac72a2","tid":565494,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"最後互射左幾多次？"},{"pid":"120289552838fc722d71d17dde807495f804e223","tid":565494,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d574efb8ae3cc0c6e113d3c60daeec34cac72a2","tid":565494,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"最後互射左幾多次？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-2